E2kOperation

<!-- ##### SECTION Short_Description ##### -->
Cancellable operation support

<!-- ##### SECTION Long_Description ##### -->
<para>
#E2kOperation represents a handle which can be used to cancel a
pending operation (where the operation may be composed of several
cancellable steps).
</para>

